      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a compression method based on the LZS compression algorithm.  This document defines the application of the LZS algorithm to the IP Payload Compression Protocol.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
